headline: ICE’s Futures and Options Markets Reach Record Open Interest of 114 Million Contracts
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK & LONDON & AMSTERDAM, January 29, 2026--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced record open interest (OI) across its global futures and options markets of over 114 million contracts on January 26, 2026, up approximately 20% year-over-year (y/y).
